race.comment: MONTY'S RETURN (4) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from four starts. Missed the frame latest (19.52) when fifth over 350m at this track in a Restricted WIN. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. MISS CHARMED (1) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, paving the way for a 1.5 lengths win at this track over 350m in 19.61. Capable of going well again. DINOSAUR DEANO (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 19.58 beating Gumtree Hill. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Significant danger. WHITE SHIRAZ (6) can play a role in the finish without surprising.
